##The story of the epidemic in the film of the workmates 01: The cooks who have been idled at home

Micro-signal kidsdoit

Function introduction, practice school (Beijing Xixi Children Care Center Vocational Training Department) , is a 15-18-year-old migrant children full-time, non-academic vocational education public welfare projects. The mission and vision are: to explore new career development paths for the children of migrant workers, and to cultivate "precious ordinary people" for a good society.

EDITOR'S NOTE

Editor's note

Starting from 2019, practical schools for migrant workers' children and Magnolia Flowers for female workers have co-organized a writing class for female workers with the support of the Ginkgo Partnership Fund, and last week launched a series of articles on "epidemic in the pen of female workers" . Recently, I have received many pictures and home life stories from the workers.

We collate a part, publish, welcome everybody to read, also welcome everybody to give a tip (reward meeting passes to author) . Your encouragement is very important. Thank you!

"female workers under the epidemic" will also continue to collate the launch, please look forward to.

Photo and caption by Ho man-king. A 47-year-old native of Suining, Sichuan Province, at the end of this year. Twenty-one years in Beijing, 17,18 years as a housekeeper.

Friday, February 28,2020, was a sunny day. Many days not out of the Community Gate Iron Railings, this afternoon the sun is particularly large, and relative home wench out to buy fish, dinner "old thing" (refers to the author's husband) do green pepper boiled fish. Passing by the rape flower field, the flowers are very bright, suddenly saw a bee busy in the honey, hurriedly took out the mobile phone from the pocket, "Click" to take that moment, hurriedly share to my (Mulan) sisters, ha Ha still"rape flower""oil"hair wrong, happy, excited!

Thursday, February 27,2020. My son wanted wonton soup, so I bought fresh meat and chopped it into meat with a kitchen knife. "Young Master" can not pack, "old thing" , "old woman" , "big young master" , we three people pack together, pack more than one hundred and fifty, all ate up special incense, my home is not a git

On the morning of February 26,2020, my "old man" got up and cooked the GRUEL. I was still in bed. He went to the bed in the bedroom and said, "today I want to eat your cake. " I said, "No problem. " I immediately got up and washed my hands and made flour, cut The diced bell pepper and put it in. Add the pepper, salt and two eggs. Stir together. Pan Heat, oil, and then use a spoon, one into the pot; a small fire slowly fried, and then with a shovel, fried on both sides of the Golden Brown. One Word, "incense" ! Three words, "extra fragrant" !

Photo and caption by Huang Yinju, a native of Yiyang, Hunan Province. I have worked in Dongguan for more than 20 years. I came to Beijing two years ago. I'm a chef in the practical school.

The end of the year, because of the "epidemic" impact at home, he usually has not been at home without vegetables, also can not go out to buy vegetables. Often relatives, friends and neighbors bring me food and delicious food. Sometimes a pile of food comes to the door, and you don't even know who it's from. So, I always think in my heart, people often send me this and that, always feeling uneasy, always feeling that I owe a lot to others.

And children live in the north for many years, the son is like to eat meat loaf, the daughter likes to eat flower roll, may also have two sister and brother have a habit of living in the north! I Miss Pasta all the time. I was bored at home anyway. The epidemic is a little better now. Went to the supermarket and bought a bag of flour. The evening of the dough, the next morning to get up early to see the wake-up hair like cotton-like dough heart warm inside. And then I called my cousin over, and I showed her how to do it, and when I was done, I steamed it with Wood. WHOA! It's beautiful. It's beautiful. Delicious steamed bread, steamed stuffed Bun, flower roll.

Later, when the steamed buns were hot, they were served to the villagers from house to house. And that they're sorry for my love... because there's always more food. It's still rotten, and I can't bear to throw it away. Plus people sent me too much to eat, see people so warm-hearted treatment, but also ashamed to refuse, it is too bad! Rotten food in the evening to throw away a lot of secretly, too bad, too bad..

Photo and caption by Han Jinlong, a 40-year-old native of Lingbi County, Anhui Province, who works as a breakfast teacher.

Back to Beijing has been more than a month, from the beginning of the wait-and-see, experienced a boring crazy, now, has been able to face the daily life of a snail. I'm supposed to be a chef, so I figured out a way to cook.

First put in the home more than a year of raw sunflower seeds turned out, stir-fry for nearly an hour. In the movie, hands are not idle, the peanut peeled, boiled five-spice peanuts to do, fried peanuts also done, and later, the peanut fried, put on the icing, sprinkle sesame seeds, also done.

Finish with peanuts, began to think about three meals a day, the routine is the night before steamed a pot of rice, stir-fry a large number of dishes. Dishes are potatoes, cabbage, or potatoes, cabbage, Vermicelli and fish Tofu stew in a pot, the main role of the potato cabbage. One is because a while ago the food is scarce, there is no food, is also very expensive, that is, these dishes cheap, easy to preserve.

This pot of rice can eat a third the night before, the next morning with leftover rice boil more than three bowls of porridge, porridge, and then put three eggs in a pot to cook. There was porridge and eggs boiling, and here I began to cook the "sloughing" .

Get Jin to put the noodles, put two eggs inside, and then put Salt, incense, chopped scallions, and then put the right amount of water, stir into thin soup with chopsticks. Take a pot ignition, pour a little oil, turn the pot so that the oil over the bottom of the pot, the oil is also hot, smoking. Pour the flour into the bottom of the pot.

Then turn the pot, watching the soup in the bottom of the pot solidification, and then along the bottom of the solidification of the pot, a circle to turn up, and then slowly solidification.

It took more than a minute to get from the white noodle soup to the sallow bread. At this time and then turn the bottom of the Pan, the whole cake is off the bottom of the pan. Then it is the technical work, the whole cake in the Pan when all over! Cook it again and it's ready to go. In my hometown, it is called "flour and flour Bun" , and in Beijing it is called "burnt-down cake" .

When the porridge is cooked, a pile of chips will be finished!

The happiest thing is to have breakfast together as a family. This atmosphere gives one a feeling of peace and stability.

Editor: Yeung yik-kum
PLATE MAKING: Lin Chuhong
